      <h2>Short Bio</h2>
      <p>Jay Trainer is a Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania singer-songwriter whose music sits where folk, acoustic rock, Americana, and room-first storytelling meet. His catalog spans eight releases and nearly two decades, from <em>The Waking Hours</em> to <em>A Whisper Of Ruin — Deluxe Edition</em>.</p>
      <p>The songs are rooted in place, memory, resilience, and the instinct to keep going. Briar Patch Records is the independent label home for Jay Trainer's complete catalog.</p>
    </div>
